snippet.title: 3 Ex-Girlfriends Describe Their Relationship With the Same Man - Shawn Foxx | Glamour
snippet.description:
We brought in three of Shawn's exes, Marissa, Amber, and Shavante to ask each of them about their experience dating him. What's his favorite place to eat? What was he first attracted to about each of them? What were their nicknames? What is his most used emoji? What new things did they introduce each other to? What did they think of each other's friends? Why did they break up? Find out all that and more in "All My Exes."
